HEADWORD: Wagenboom
<hw>Wa"gen*boom`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D., literally,
wagon tree.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A south African proteaceous
tree (<spn>Protea grandiflora</spn>); also, its tough wood, used for
making wagon wheels.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

